 Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">易于使用。<span lang=\"EN-US\">ATM</span>系统的操作应当尽量简洁，并且伴有足够的提示信息。让使用者可以在初次使用本系统的情况下就可以安全高效地进行账户操作。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">低故障率。针对可能出现的各种异常情况，<span lang=\"EN-US\">ATM</span>系统拥有详尽的检测和处理机制。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri\">1.2<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">定义<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:66.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">ATMClient</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">：<span lang=\"EN-US\">ATM</span>客户层<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:66.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">ATMServer: ATM</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">服务层<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:66.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">QuerySubSystem: </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">查询子系统<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:66.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">WithdrawSubSystem: </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">取款子系统<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:66.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">TransferSubSystem:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">转账子系统<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:66.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">DepositSubSystem:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">存款子系统<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:66.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">ModifyAccountInfoSubSystem:</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">账户信息更改子系统<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:66.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">l<span style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">DATABASE</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">：数据库<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l1 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri\">1.3<span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">概述<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">在这个文档中，我们给出<span lang=\"EN-US\">ATM</span>系统的具体系统设计，主要包括标识子系统、提供访问控制、设计全局控制流、标识访问控制、标识边界条件和标识服务。其中各个子系统服务由<span lang=\"EN-US\">UML</span>构件图标识求精。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>','297ec0504e8f8134014e8fd47dd30005',0,'超级管理员','2015-07-15 11:49:11','超级管理员','2015-07-15 11:50:23'),('297ec0504e8f8134014e8fd50d130007','297eb7974e867694014e86cbee820004','2.建议软件体系结构','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">2.1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\n宋体;color:black\">子系统分解：</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:red\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">我们从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ATM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">系统的功能需求和分析模型中对子系统进行标识。这一活动的目的是将系统分解成自含的构件，这些构件应该是自治的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">我们选择了典型的三层体系结构的风格来设计我们</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ATM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">系统，通过一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ATMClient</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">的子系统来为用户提供前端的启动所有与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ATM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">操作有关的用例，在应用的逻辑层，我们创建一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ATMServer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">的子系统来接受用户通过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ATMClient</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">子系统发送过来的各种操作请求，而</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ATMServer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">子系统则是具体的调用执行我们设计的各种用例，包括</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">QuerySubSystem</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">WithdrawSubSystem</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TransferSubSystem</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">DepositSubSystem</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ModifyAccountInfoSubSystem</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri\">，而针对具体的实现，我们在存储层提供